snippet.title: Detana Twinbee Yahoo! Deluxe Pack (出たなツインビーヤッホー！ＤＥＬＵＸＥ ＰＡＣＫ). [Saturn]. 1CC. HARD. 60Fps.
snippet.description:
Detana Twinbee Yahoo! Deluxe Pack (出たなツインビーヤッホー！ＤＥＬＵＸＥ ＰＡＣＫ). [Saturn]. 1CC. HARD. 60Fps.
:- Played BY PiE. - "May 2nd, 2020".
.
A compilation of Twinbee games, and was released for the Sega Saturn by Konami. It contains the arcade shooters Detana!! Twinbee and Twinbee Yahoo!.
